      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BORDER BEAST (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.4 lengths at Warragul in a handy 22.87 beating Lady Persimmon. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Hard to go past. VIENNA ON SHOW (2) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at this track over 435m behind Tick Returns (25.11) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Leading chance. GO STEVIE (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (25.09) in a Grade 5 H at this track. Has a good record here including nine wins. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. PAW XYLA (8) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
